metadata.name: LotteryTicketNFT
metadata.description: This NFT ticket is a lottery ticket that will provide you with the opportunity to win up to 5ETH! Winners will be chosen at random and you may win anywhere from 0.05ETH - 5ETH. (Only one person will win the 5ETH) prize. May the odds be in your favor! If this ticket earns volume on OS then random ETH drop will be added only for the lucky chosen ones.
